1、一般做形容词的名词用单数,除非这个名词总是以附属形式使用：data analysis,sports injury
cells membrane   改为cell membrane
nanoparticles suspensions solution  改为nanoparticle suspension solution
reactions mechanisms   改为reaction mechanisms

2、数字的写法：
(1) 小于10的整数用英文，大于等于10的数字用阿拉伯数字
three experiments
23 birds
(2) 有小数点和单位的数字用阿拉伯数字
1.2 hours
5 percent
page 3
(3) 句子开头的数字用英文字
10 ml ethanol was added./Ten ml ethanol was added.    改为Ethanol(10ml)was added.
30 eggs were used daily during the study.   改为   During the study,30 eggs were used daily.
(4) 两个数字前后并列出现时，一个用英文字
there 8-rat groups
two 5-day study
12 two-engine airplanes
(5) 小于1的数字的单位用单数，大于1的数字的单位用复数；
0.25 gram;1.5grams
零后面的单位用复数；
zero meters      
0 meters
单位的缩写单数和复数一样;
0.1 mL 
15 mL

